meaning: Her eyebrows are inexplicably beautiful. They are the gateways for infinite bliss.
commentary: From the beauty in Her face we derive calmness, joy and peace. Her beauty of her eyebrows has been described in nama 17 ‘वदनस्मर-माङ्गल्य-गृहतोरण-चिल्लिकाऽ। (‘Vadanasmara-māṅgalya-gṛhatoraṇa-cillikā’.)
